disclaimer.bullet.text.1 = there are no appropriate facilities available for you to perform your job on your employer’s premises
disclaimer.bullet.text.2 = the nature of the job requires you to live so far from the employer’s premises that it is unreasonable for you to travel to those premises on a daily basis
disclaimer.bullet.text.3 = you are required, under government restrictions, to work from home
